subject: Track and Field
Pole Vault
lead_paragraph: Victories by Kenenisa Bekele (men’s 10,000 meters) and Shelly-Ann Fraser (women’s 100) at the world championships were no surprise; a loss by the pole-vaulter Yelena Isinbayeva was.
